organic.title: 5Rock Ranch Home
organic.snippet: 5Rock Ranch is 108 beautiful acres set in the foothills of the Coast Range in Yamhill County, Oregon, about 60 miles from Portland.

organic.title: Directions | 5Rock Ranch
organic.snippet: Go about 1.2 miles to the end of the road. The 5Rock Lodge is on the right. FROM THE SOUTH: Take I-5 north and exit at # 278 Aurora/Donald.
